subject: Re: [EVP-ITC] My site is gone!
author: Frank Sumption
full_text:
I don't know, kinda strange, and suspicious since the site's been up since 
2002! It's been my expereince if you try to wake too many up, or put out 
what is percieved as good, or light energy, you get these darkside 
reactions. I learned first hand you don't try to fill an area with positve 
energy, or try to drive out all the demons, the consequences can be deadly 
as you get a darkside reaction. An Italian researcher thought he would have 
a group focus on a small area in Italy to see if conditions could be 
improved, the result, that giant quake in Afkanistan, I think it was 
directly related. I tried to surround Denver with a "shield" of white light, 
years ago, and a whole family was beaten to death with a hammer that night. 
Ya have to be really careful, cuz innocents die as a result. I wouldn't be 
surprised if loss of my son wasn't karma.  Maybe I'm thinking too much......

I'm not in a huge hurry to get the site back up, I think I need to meditate 
on this for awhile.

Frank
